               <scopecontent id="aspace_0125a43b86defd03d0ca6447de18a04c">
                  <head>Scope and Contents</head>
                  <p>109 autograph postcards signed with 9 typed letters signed, includes originals and typescript annotated copies made by Feis. Enclosed with letter of 5 August 1923 autograph manuscripts of poem "Islands," with letter of 28 November 1927, autograph manuscripts of poems "For October" and "The Thorn Trees"</p>
